            <title>[SPARK-36733] Perf issue in SchemaPruning when a struct has many fields</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-36733</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Seeing a significant performance&#160;degradation in query processing when a table contains a significantly large number of fields (&amp;gt;10K).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s the stacktraces while processing a query&lt;/p&gt;
